text: Frederick or Fred Dean may refer to: ==Sports== * Frederick Dean (rugby union) (1880–1946), Cornish rugby union player * Fred Dean (1952–2020), American football defensive end * Fred Dean (offensive lineman) (born 1955), American football guard * Fred Dean (Australian footballer) (1909–1989), Australian rules footballer ==Other== * Frederick Dean (SA Navy) (1900–1983), South African military commander * Frederick James Dean (1868-1941), British trade unionist
